<item>
            <title>[MAHOUT-807] Wrong prefixes in PrefixAdditionFilter</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MAHOUT-807</link>
                <project id="12310751" key="MAHOUT">Mahout</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The org.apache.mahout.text.PrefixAdditionFilter is not working as intended. The prefix is computed wrong when there is recursion (this is when there is at least one subdirectory).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I think the line:&lt;br/&gt;
fs.listStatus(fst.getPath(), new PrefixAdditionFilter(getConf(), getPrefix() + Path.SEPARATOR + current.getName(), getOptions(), writer, fs));&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;should better be:&lt;br/&gt;
fs.listStatus(fst.getPath(), new PrefixAdditionFilter(getConf(), getPrefix() + Path.SEPARATOR + current.getName() + Path.SEPARATOR + fst.getPath().getName(), getOptions(), writer, fs));&lt;/p&gt;</description>
